USER STORY: Accessing Personalized AI Workout Motivation (Golden Path)


AS A user,
 I WANT TO log in and access my profile with my workout streak and goals, then start a personalized AI voice workout session,
 SO THAT I can receive motivation from a chosen celebrity voice tailored to my goals and continue building my workout streak.
SCENARIO: User Logs In and Accesses Profile
GIVEN the user opens the iSpeak app,
 WHEN the user selects "Log In" and enters valid credentials,
 THEN the system should authenticate the user through Firebase
 WITHIN 3 seconds,
 AND redirect the user to their profile screen
 WITHIN 2 seconds.

SCENARIO: Viewing Workout Streak and Goals
GIVEN the user is on their profile screen,
 WHEN the profile page loads,
 THEN the system should display the user’s current workout streak (number of consecutive workout days)
 WITHIN 2 seconds,
 AND display the user’s saved personal goals and rewards that will be used for AI-generated motivation.

SCENARIO: Continue Streak Button Navigation
GIVEN the user is on their profile screen,
 WHEN the user clicks the "Continue Streak" button,
 THEN the system should navigate the user to the AI Voice Setup screen
 WITHIN 2 seconds.
SCENARIO: Selecting Voice and Intensity
GIVEN the user is on the AI Voice Setup screen,
 WHEN the user selects a preferred celebrity voice persona from the available options,
 AND selects a motivation intensity mode (Light, Standard, or Intense),
 THEN the system should save the selected preferences for the session
 WITHIN 1 second,
 AND enable the "Start Session" button.

SCENARIO: Starting AI Voice Workout Session
GIVEN the user has selected a voice persona and intensity level,
 WHEN the user clicks the "Start Session" button,
 THEN the system should generate a personalized motivational script using the user’s saved goals and rewards
 WITHIN 3 seconds,
 AND begin playing AI-generated voice motivation audio
 WITHIN 5 seconds,
 AND start the workout timer for the session.
